# The move command executed successfully, and I am now back at the position (0, 0).
# I will now attempt to find the nearest stone resource again and move toward it step by step to ensure I can place the stone furnace correctly.

# Finding the nearest stone resource position again.
stone_patch_position = nearest(Resource.Stone)  # Looking for the nearest stone resource position.
print(f'Nearest stone position: {stone_patch_position}')  # Outputting the nearest stone position.

# Attempting to move to the nearest stone position.
move_to(stone_patch_position)  # Move to the nearest stone resource.
